  <brief_title>Shuttle Walk Test Performed on a Treadmill Versus a Corridor in Patients With COPD</brief_title>
  <acronym>(SWTiCOPD)</acronym>
  <official_title>Analysis of Metabolic and Ventilatory Demands During the Shuttle Walk Test Performed on a Treadmill Versus a Corridor in Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD)</official_title>
